{"tid":749964,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"12月龍珠劇場版，大波蓮搵邊個明星配先有霸氣？","createTime":"2018-07-20T12:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T12:52:26.000Z","uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c84bb883653ef797288c4101355852df931fafc7","tid":749964,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:55:21.000Z","msg":"雖然電視版都有其他人配過，但最深入民心一定係叮噹<br />\n原電影配 叮噹已不在人世<br />\n<br />\n而通常而家鐘意搵明星配電影動畫boss<br />\n特別大波蓮目前係空缺<br />\n<br />\n為左各位龍珠迷自己著想<br />\n又希望香港有關方面有所參考，搵岩人配音 <br />\n所以有需要提早五個月研究一下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d78eecfb5627a84bbb8f5c47771e93ced10850","tid":749964,"uid":17008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T13:10:23.000Z","msg":"邊個先carry到布洛尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db07bf9c0cee9a4837a75dc4e1ca123a9b34a3ce","tid":749964,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"松岡禎丞"},{"pid":"a7292812b3b5e8e6bf54ac18857438c4a5d03bba","tid":749964,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461f278213e7472223bda11790ecfc6dc1dea971","tid":749964,"uid":35112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:44:33.000Z","msg":"第二集果時係atv路飛配"},{"pid":"ea4b4a236818b00ae56d6b907f2ec7f667fec020","tid":749964,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/6/61/KN4R8.gif/revision/latest?cb=20131011190813\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F6%2F61%2FKN4R8.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20131011190813&h=be3cfbb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n諗起呢幅gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br